latestPosts.caption:
Experienced the most beautiful stay at Jumeirah Gulf of Bahrain, and I honestly didn’t expect to fall in love with the place this much. The rooms were sea-facing and super cozy, the food was incredible including the breakfast spread that became my daily highlight — and I even tried my first-ever hammam, which was beyond relaxing. The property has seven pools, a private beach, and even a private island. And if you’re planning a big fat Indian wedding, this place is made for it. With private villas that open up directly to the beach, it’s luxury and celebration wrapped in one unforgettable location.
@jumeirahgulfofbahrain @tourismbh @jumeirah
